msgid ""
"When a nerve cell transmits a chemical message to a muscle, muscle cells "
"contract, causing a bone to move. When someone receives a blow to their "
"head, part of their brain is compressed, some memories might be lost or "
"confused, and the person will be at higher risk for other brain injuries. "
"When a child touches his finger to a hot pan, A nerve impulse is sent "
"immediately to his brain, causing him to withdraw his hand. Read on to learn "
"more about how animals respond."
msgstr ""
"Cuando una célula nerviosa transmite un mensaje químico a un músculo, "
"células musculares se contraen, causando un hueso moverse. Cuando alguien "
"recibe un golpe en la cabeza, una parte de su cerebro se comprime, algunos "
"recuerdos pueden ser perdidos o confundidos, y la persona va a estar en "
"mayor riesgo de otras lesiones cerebrales. Cuando un niño toca el dedo de "
"una sartén caliente, un impulso nervioso se envía inmediatamente al cerebro, "
"causándole a retirar la mano. Siga leyendo para aprender más acerca de cómo "
"los animales responden."

msgid ""
"When a nerve cell transmits a chemical message to a muscle, muscle cells "
"contract, causing a bone to move. When someone receives a blow to their "
"head, part of their brain is compressed, some memories might be lost or "
"confused, and the person will be at higher risk for other brain injuries. "
"When a child touches his finger to a hot pan, a nerve impulse is sent "
"immediately to his brain, causing him to withdraw his hand. Read on to learn "
